for the object, based on policy decisions.
""" .

<http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/preservation/preservationLevelRole/req> a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:label "REQUIREMENT" ;
    rdfs:subClassOf valuesets:PreservationLevelRole ;
    skos:definition """The preservation level required by the depositor or
